metadata.name: Please become ART
metadata.description:
- Please become ART
- Nope
- Why not?
- Just because lol
- …

For years, I constantly heard this conversation in my head. Now it seems that I might get the opposite response.

All I've ever wanted was to create art—to let out whatever was screaming in my head and to resonate it with others'. I found the sign for this path, and I took my first step onto it.
